OL,3,CForeign Secretary defends decision to
OL,4,Callow US to use UK bases for Iran
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,8,Fdefended the government's decision to
OL,9,Fallow the US to use British military
OL,10,Fbases for "defensive" strikes in Iran.
OL,12,FThe foreign secretary said the UK
OL,13,F"continues to support diplomatic
OL,14,Fprocesses" in Iran, but "it's
OL,15,Fimportant we make sure there's
OL,16,Fdefensive support in the short term."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
