FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772503387
OL,3,CForeign Secretary defends decision to
OL,4,Callow US to use UK bases for Iran
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer announced on Sunday
OL,8,Fthat the UK would give the US
OL,9,Fpermission to use the bases after
OL,10,Freports that he previously denied such
OL,11,Frequests.
OL,13,FThe PM specified that British forces
OL,14,Fwould not be directly involved in the
OL,15,Fstrikes, and the bases would only be
OL,16,Fused for the "specific and limited
OL,17,Fdefensive purpose" of targeting
OL,18,Fmissile storage depots and launchers
OL,19,Fbeing used to attack Iran's neighbours.
OL,26,@xD@NOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
