FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772503387
OL,3,CForeign Secretary defends decision to
OL,4,Callow US to use UK bases for Iran
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FUS President Donald Trump said he was
OL,8,F"very disappointed" in Starmer's
OL,9,Finitial decision not to allow the use
OL,10,Fof British bases like Diego Garcia in
OL,11,Fthe Chagos Islands.
OL,13,FIn an interview with The Telegraph
OL,14,Fpublished on Monday, Trump said that
OL,15,FStarmer "took far too long" to change
OL,16,Fhis mind.
OL,18,F"That's probably never happened
OL,19,Fbetween our countries before," he
OL,20,Fsaid, adding: "It sounds like he was
OL,21,Fworried about the legality."
OL,26,@wD@[O]zD@AOU{D@^O]|D@OOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772503387
OL,3,CForeign Secretary defends decision to
OL,4,Callow US to use UK bases for Iran
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FCooper told ITV News on Monday that
OL,8,FIranian missile launchers are being
OL,9,Fused "to target areas where we have
OL,10,Fhundreds of thousands of British
OL,11,Fcitizens and where British interests
OL,12,Fare being hugely affected by what is
OL,13,Fhappening.
OL,15,F"That's why it's so important that
OL,16,Fdefensive support is provided, and
OL,17,Fthis is simply about the use of UK
OL,18,Fbases," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
