OL,3,CForeign Secretary defends decision to
OL,4,Callow US to use UK bases for Iran
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FA British base in Cyprus was hit by a
OL,8,Fdrone on Sunday, striking RAF Akrotiri
OL,9,Fhours after the PM announced American
OL,10,Fforces could use the UK bases. ITV
OL,11,FNews understands the drone was
OL,12,Flaunched before Starmer made the
OL,13,Fannouncement.
OL,15,FOfficials said the damage inflicted on
OL,16,FAkrotiri by the kamikaze drone was
OL,17,F"minimal" and there were no
OL,18,Fcasualties, while family members of
OL,19,Fpersonnel had been moved away from the
OL,20,Fbase as a precaution.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
