OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772503387
OL,3,CForeign Secretary defends decision to
OL,4,Callow US to use UK bases for Iran
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FStarmer insisted the UK had "learned
OL,8,Fthe lessons of Iraq" in his statement
OL,9,Fon Sunday, but Cooper was pressed on
OL,10,Fwhether the UK is being "dragged into
OL,11,Fanother war" by the US.
OL,13,FCooper said the government wants to
OL,14,Fsee a "negotiated agreement that
OL,15,Fprevents any nuclear development by
OL,16,Fthe Iranian regime," but stressed
OL,17,F"it's important we can make sure
OL,18,Fthere's defensive support in the short
OL,19,Fterm right now to partner countries
OL,20,Fwhere so many British citizens are
OL,21,Fliving."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
