CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772503387
OL,3,CForeign Secretary defends decision to
OL,4,Callow US to use UK bases for Iran
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FAround 300,000 Britons are believed to
OL,8,Fbe in countries targeted by Iran, with
OL,9,F102,000 registered with the Foreign
OL,10,FOffice for updates as officials
OL,11,Fexamine all options, including a
OL,12,Fpotential mass evacuation.
OL,14,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,15,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,16,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,17,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
